00:27:09.810 --> 00:27:11.490
really like the pictures.

00:27:11.490 --> 00:27:14.084
That's great.

00:27:14.084 --> 00:27:16.370
AUDIENCE: What's your favorite
beer bar in the city?

00:27:16.370 --> 00:27:19.180
JOSH BERNSTEIN: My beer
bar in the city?

