Since I'm a cheap bastard, I
like Beer Craft, because you

00:27:21.700 --> 00:27:23.980
can buy a growler of beer, and
then you can share with

00:27:23.980 --> 00:27:25.380
people, and it's like--

00:27:25.380 --> 00:27:30.370
as far as in the city, beer
bars I like going to--

00:27:30.370 --> 00:27:32.170
you know, Blind Tiger is
nice, but I can never

00:27:32.170 --> 00:27:33.120
actually get in there.

00:27:33.120 --> 00:27:34.340
And I don't like--

