It's nice.

00:28:02.230 --> 00:28:04.960
But living in Brooklyn, going up
to Upper East Side, for a--

00:28:04.960 --> 00:28:05.880
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE].

00:28:05.880 --> 00:28:06.950
JOSH BERNSTEIN: Oh,
so easy for you.

00:28:06.950 --> 00:28:07.850
For me, I got to--

00:28:07.850 --> 00:28:10.180
I work out of my house, so it's
