00:29:20.230 --> 00:29:21.100
Yeah, but it's every--

00:29:21.100 --> 00:29:22.580
like, every week, a
new thing pops up.

00:29:22.580 --> 00:29:23.860
And we're going to
see a ton new--

00:29:23.860 --> 00:29:25.910
a ton new breweries coming
online, too,

00:29:25.910 --> 00:29:26.640
this year, I think.

00:29:26.640 --> 00:29:28.900
Especially within
the New York--

00:29:28.900 --> 00:29:30.980
not just in New York City, but
around in Long Island,

00:29:30.980 --> 00:29:33.180
breweries coming in upstate New
York that are going to be

00:29:33.180 --> 00:29:34.510
coming into the city.

00:29:34.510 --> 00:29:36.480
It's a pretty great time
to be a craft beer

00:29:36.480 --> 00:29:37.086
fan in New York City.

00:29:37.086 --> 00:29:38.336
Let me tell ya.

